<i>Lama kita tak jumpa.</i>

28
00:01:01,386 --> 00:01:04,116
<i>Kalian yang terakhir kali bicara</i>
<i>dengan Jun-seo di telepon.</i>

29
00:01:04,141 --> 00:01:06,178
<i>Won Jong-soo, Park Tae-jin,</i>
<i>Oh Chi-hyun.</i>

30
00:01:06,228 --> 00:01:09,654
<i>Mereka mengalami pahit dan manis</i>
