67
00:03:15,027 --> 00:03:16,471
Ayo pergi. Di sini dingin.

68
00:03:28,631 --> 00:03:30,431
Ji-yeon.

69
00:03:31,405 --> 00:03:32,191
Ya?

70
00:03:32,313 --> 00:03:34,471
Aku sudah memikirkannya lagi.

71
00:03:35,661 --> 00:03:39,008
Bagaimana kalau kita minta
Jun-seo diautopsi?

72
00:03:40,179 --> 00:03:40,913
Apa?

73
00:03:41,305 --> 00:03:42,341
